                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/4.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>Himachal pradesh</h3>
                        <p>The top things to do in Himachal pradesh are Manali, Shimla, Mcleodganj and more...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/5.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>Dalhousie</h3>
