                </div>
                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/6.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Kodaikanal </h3>
                        <p>Kodaikanal is a hill town in the southern Indian state of Tamil Nadu.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/7.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>Delhi</h3>
                        <p>Delhi showcases an ancient culture and a rapidly modernising country.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/8.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Ooty </h3>
                        <p>Ooty is a resort town in the Western Ghats mountains, in southern India's Tamil Nadu state.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/9.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> kerla </h3>
                        <p>Kerala is famous especially for its ecotourism initiatives and beautiful backwaters.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/10.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>Kanyakumari</h3>
                        <p>Kanyakumari is a coastal town in the state of Tamil Nadu on India's southern tip.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/11.jpeg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3>Araku Valley</h3>
                        <p>Araku Valley is a hill station and valley region in the southeastern Indian state of Andhra
                            Pradesh</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="zoom-in">
                    <img src="/img/images/pack_img/13.jpg" alt="">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Agra </h3>
                        <p>One of the seven wonders of the world, Taj Mahal is located on the banks of River Yamuna in
                            Agra...</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- gallery section starts here -->

        <!-- places section starts here -->
        <section class="places" id="places">
            <h1 class="heading">
                <span>p</span>
                <span>l</span>
                <span>a</span>
                <span>c</span>
                <span>e</span>
                <span>s</span>
            </h1>

            <div class="box-container">
                <div class="box" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <img src="/img/places/types/beach.jpg" alt="Beach">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Beach </h3>
                        <p>Beach areas are popular types of tourist destinations. Some people travel a long way to reach
                            a
                            beach</p>
                        <a href="/places/viewplaces/beach" class="btn">see more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <img src="/img/places/types/island.jpg" alt="Islands">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Islands </h3>
