                        </p>
                        <a href="/places/viewplaces/island" class="btn">see more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <img src="/img/places/types/hillStation.jpg" alt="Hill Station">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Hill Stations </h3>
                        <p>There are many different activities that you can do in the mountains, such as hiking, skiing,
                            horse riding, and more.</p>
                        <a href="/places/viewplaces/hillStation" class="btn">see more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <img src="/img/places/types/forest.jpg" alt="Forest">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Forest </h3>
                        <p>There are forests all over the world, although the flora and fauna differs according to the
