                        <a href="/places/viewplaces/forest" class="btn">see more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <img src="/img/places/types/winter.jpg" alt="Winter">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Snow </h3>
                        <p>People travel to destinations with winter conditions for a range of winter sport activities.
                        </p>
                        <a href="/places/viewplaces/snow" class="btn">see more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <img src="/img/places/types/cultural.jpg" alt="Cultural">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Cultural </h3>
                        <p>A type of tourism activity in which the visitor's essential motivation is to learn, discover,
                            experience.</p>
                        <a href="/places/viewplaces/traditional" class="btn">see more</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="box" data-aos="fade-left">
                    <img src="/img/places/types/Desert.jpg" alt="Desert">
                    <div class="content">
                        <h3> Desert </h3>
                        <p>Desert is an undulating sand plain covered with sand dunes.</p>
                        <a href="/places/viewplaces/desert" class="btn">see more</a>
